      "description": "Affordable fixer-upper that runs and can make a solid project or budget transportation for the right buyer. This car is in poor condition overall, with heavy cosmetic wear and clear signs of age inside and out, and it will need repairs and attention. That said, it\u2019s a straightforward, inexpensive option for someone handy who wants a low-cost car with potential.",
