    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Fair-condition used car priced accordingly. It shows noticeable wear inside and out, including cosmetic imperfections and signs of regular use, but it remains a decent, usable vehicle overall. The interior is serviceable, the exterior has visible age and blemishes, and buyers should expect an older car that is not perfect but can still be a practical option for someone shopping on value.",
