      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next owner, this vehicle offers straightforward value for anyone seeking dependable basic transportation without a big investment. It shows its age cosmetically and mechanically, but it remains a practical opportunity for a handy buyer, commuter, or project-minded shopper looking for low-cost entry into ownership. Priced to move and represented honestly, this is a sensible option for buyers who prioritize affordability.",
      "price": 4995.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with some life left in it? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it starts, runs, and could be a great fit for someone who needs basic transportation or wants a simple project to tinker with. I\u2019m being upfront that it shows its age and will need some attention, but for the money, it\u2019s a solid opportunity to get into a car without spending a fortune. If you\u2019re practical and know how to make the most of a used vehicle, this one could be a great little buy.",
      "price": 4800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Driver-grade project with a strong-running engine, responsive automatic transmission, and dependable road manners. Not a show car, but it starts, moves out well, and offers a solid mechanical foundation for someone who wants an affordable daily, weekend fixer, or parts-friendly platform. Recent upkeep has helped keep it usable, and the chassis still feels composed enough to enjoy. Cosmetic wear and age-related flaws are present, but for the money this is a capable, honest car with plenty of life left for the next owner.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap entry point. Not pretty, but it gets the job done. Priced to move.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A true diamond-in-the-rough for the right buyer, this car has the kind of lived-in character you can\u2019t fake. It\u2019s the sort of ride that feels like it still has stories left to tell\u2014perfect for someone who sees possibility where others just see age. Whether you\u2019re after a budget-friendly project, a practical runaround, or something to make your own, this one offers a chance to get behind the wheel without spending big. Honest, approachable, and full of potential, it\u2019s ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Affordable and straightforward, this vehicle is a practical choice for buyers seeking low-cost transportation or a solid project opportunity. It shows its age and wear, but it still offers real value at an accessible price point. If you want an inexpensive vehicle with potential and no pretense, this one deserves a look.",
      "price": 4950.0,
